snippet.title: Final Fantasy Tactics [trailer]
snippet.description: So this is  trailer of FFT a tactical Japanese RPG. Fun game but hard and frustrating. I played FFT few times but never to the end, but I know people that loves it. Someday I must concentrate and end it.
